### Create user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "pedro",
  "email": "pedro@example.com",
  "password": "test123",
  "enabled": true,
  "roleIds": [1, 2]
}

### Get users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users

